# Security — Cross-cutting Rules

## Frontend security

**[SKILL_SECURITY_FRONTEND]** — invoke when touching build config, env vars, sourcemaps, client auth.

## Backend auth

Read security area doc completely before touching auth, session, or access control code.

## Secrets

- Never hardcode secrets — use environment variables
- Secrets table in security area doc or `.claude/rules/secrets.md`
- Backend secrets → never exposed to frontend
- New secret → update security doc + infrastructure doc

## After modifying, update

Security changes always update security area doc.
